@baseUrl = http://localhost:3111
@contentType = application/json

### 0) サーバ起動確認（空データ想定）
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets

### 1) チケット作成（正常系）
# @name createTicket
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Payment failed on checkout",
  "description": "Customer reports card payment fails with error code PMT-402.",
  "priority": "high",
  "customerEmail": "customer@example.com"
}

### 2) 一覧確認（auto-triage 結果の反映確認）
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets

### 3) 手動トリアージ（HTTPトリガー確認）
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets/triage
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "ticketId": "TKT-1772723527561-e4a8w",
  "assignee": "support-jp-team",
  "priority": "critical"
}

### 4) 手動エスカレーション（HTTPトリガー確認）
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets/escalate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "ticketId": "TKT-1772723527561-e4a8w",
  "reason": "VIP customer impact, immediate engineering attention required"
}

### 5) 最終一覧確認（assignee/escalation情報の反映確認）
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets

### 6) バリデーションエラー確認（異常系）
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "description": "Missing title should fail",
  "priority": "medium",
  "customerEmail": "invalid-case@example.com"
}
